sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin as 관리자
    participant UI as React UI (Export)
    participant Preload as electronAPI
    participant IPC as IPC Main (setupIpcHandlers)
    participant UC as AppUseCases
    participant Dialog as Electron dialog
    participant RRepo as PrismaReservationRepository
    participant CRepo as PrismaCategoryRepository
    participant FS as Node.js fs
    participant DB as SQLite DB

    Admin->>UI: '내보내기(Export)' 사이드바 메뉴 클릭
    activate UI
    UI-->>Admin: 내보내기 설정 화면 렌더링 (카테고리 필터, 미리보기 테이블)

    Admin->>UI: '데이터 내보내기 (CSV)' 버튼 클릭
    UI->>Preload: invoke('reservation:export')
    activate Preload
    Preload->>IPC: IPC 채널 전송
    activate IPC

    IPC->>Dialog: dialog.showSaveDialog({ title, defaultPath: 'reservations.csv', filters: [csv] })
    activate Dialog
    Dialog-->>Admin: 로컬 파일 저장 탐색기(Save Dialog) 팝업 출력
    Admin->>Dialog: 저장 경로 선택 후 '저장' 클릭
    Dialog-->>IPC: { canceled: false, filePath: '/path/to/reservations.csv' }
    deactivate Dialog

    IPC->>UC: listReservations()
    activate UC
    UC->>RRepo: findAll()
    activate RRepo
    RRepo->>DB: prisma.reservation.findMany()
    activate DB
    DB-->>RRepo: Reservation[] 반환
    deactivate DB
    RRepo-->>UC: Reservation[] 반환
    deactivate RRepo
    UC-->>IPC: Reservation[] 반환
    deactivate UC

    IPC->>UC: category.findAll()
    activate UC
    UC->>CRepo: findAll()
    activate CRepo
    CRepo->>DB: prisma.category.findMany()
    activate DB
    DB-->>CRepo: Category[] 반환
    deactivate DB
    CRepo-->>UC: Category[] 반환
    deactivate CRepo
    UC-->>IPC: Category[] 반환
    deactivate UC

    Note over IPC: CSV 헤더 + 각 예약 행 생성\nr.category(숫자 ID) → 카테고리 한글명 매핑
    Note over IPC: csv = "ID,카테고리,자원명,...\n" + 각 row 데이터

    IPC->>FS: fs.writeFileSync(filePath, '\uFEFF' + csv, 'utf8')
    activate FS
    Note over FS: BOM(\uFEFF) 선두 삽입으로 Excel 한글 인코딩 깨짐 방지
    FS-->>IPC: 파일 저장 완료
    deactivate FS

    IPC-->>Preload: { success: true, filePath }
    deactivate IPC
    Preload-->>UI: Promise Resolve
    deactivate Preload
    UI-->>Admin: "내보내기 완료: /path/reservations.csv" 성공 알림 출력
    deactivate UI
